title: JS Code Club
details:
Details
-------

Bring your ideas, pair with other developers, and start building!

JS Code Club is open to all. If you are a seasoned developer or just starting out, and have an interest in JavaScript, join the club!

Add your project at [https://code-club.herokuapp.com/](https://code-club.herokuapp.com/) or join someone else's, or just show up ready to hack!
